# Deployment Workflow

- Treat deployment as complete only after explicit health verification.
- Confirm frontend, backend, and API endpoints are reachable post-deploy.
- Require successful service-level health checks for all critical components.
- Inspect logs for critical errors before closing a deployment task.
- Keep rollback path clear before applying production changes.
